@soupnco_sg 
I’ve just tried one of the most memorable Fish soups! It’s rich, creamy, robust and just check out the ingredients!  Ain’t going to lie folks! A picture paints a thousand words and in this case, What you see is what you get! Huge Prawns, crispy chunks of fried fish, smooth milky savory soup, silky rice noodles!
🔻
@soupnco_sg is a home-based business offering authentic Malaysian comfort food such as Fish soup, Curry noodles! (Yes! Curry noodles! Try it too!) Curry Chee Cheong Fun, and addictive sides such as hand made Fish cakes, prawn rolls and more! It’s definitely worth trying judging by the attention and passion that goes with these dishes! In other words.. IT IS SHIOK! Check out below on how you can place your orders!
